[normal]Annex 3[bold]Harris Primary Academy February 2013[bold]Letter Home for a 4 year old [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Unfortunately your child has still not met their initial target of being able to recognise numerals 1-10. Therefore your child is not making rapid progress, which is hindering 
[normal]their overall progress and attainment.
[normal]Please work hard with your child over the half term, helping them to achieve this target using the resources provided*.  If you need any more support in helping your child then please do not hesitate to see a member o
[normal]f staff.
[normal]Targets are regularly monitored so as soon as your child reaches their target we are able to set a new one and keep their progress developing at a steady pace.
[normal]Kind Regards
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]*
[normal]Pieces of paper numbered 0-10 were enclosed
